{
  "stem": "21812.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I told you about the doctor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there were a lot of others.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you know, I was 14 years old, just not even 14 when Hitler came in-- probably 13.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had my friends and my own life and school life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I really wasn't in contact with-- with the outside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I didn't really-- well, unless I-- possibly I'm repressing it, but I don't think-- I mean, we talked about it constantly because we knew it was going on and we know what was happening in Germany and-- and what would be happening-- we had a pretty good idea what would be happening in Austria.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So this wasn't something that was hidden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But personal experiences, I really didn't have where I, you know, met up with [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] anybody, or I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At-- you have to-- again, we need the time frame of when-- when are you-- what are you thinking about, what-- what period?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before the Anschluss?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because there was a tremendous amount of tur-- turmoil.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was going on for a long time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Nazis-- little by little, the illegal Nazis in Austria were-- were becoming legal, almost.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were coming to the surface.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were underground, then they were coming to the surface.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And were-- there were riots and there were protest marches.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were-- as a matter of fact, one of the first incidents that happened was my uncle-- and this is my only remaining aunt, who is her husband, who is now-- she is 95 years old.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And her husband had a jewelery store, but also-- which inherited from his father.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But also, his cousin-- or second cousin, I don't recall-- also had a store.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
